entry.def: An airbrush is an artist's tool which sprays paint onto a surface.

entry.tran: 用喷枪修饰，用气笔修改（相片等）
entry.def: To airbrush a photograph or other image means to change it using an airbrush, especially to make it more beautiful or perfect.

example.tran: 用喷枪修饰过的完美躯体

example.ex: ...bits of photographs cut, pasted and then airbrushed to create a convincing whole.
example.tran: 把照片的碎片裁剪好后粘贴在一起，然后用气笔修成一个令人信以为真的整体图片

means.word_mean: 1. an atomizer to spray paint by means of compressed air
